(19, 'Bitcoin ajunge la 100.000$ &ndash; Ce urmeazÄƒ?', 'Bitcoin sub 90.000 USD &ndash; Ce urmeazÄƒ È™i cum poÈ›i profita de volatilitatea mare de pe piaÈ›Äƒ\nCriza de la &icirc;nceputul sÄƒptÄƒm&acirc;nii continuÄƒ pe piaÈ›a cripto. Bitcoin a cÄƒzut p&acirc;nÄƒ sub nivelul de 90.000 de dolari. La momentul scrierii acestui text, cea mai valoroasÄƒ criptomonedÄƒ se tranzacÈ›ioneazÄƒ la un preÈ› de 88.430 de dolari, &icirc;n scÄƒdere cu 3,67% &icirc;n decurs de o zi.\nEconomica.net - mie, 26 feb. 2025, 15:19\nTrimite pe:\nBitcoin sub 90.000 USD - Ce urmeazÄƒ È™i cum poÈ›i profita de volatilitatea mare de pe piaÈ›Äƒ\nBitcoin &icirc;È™i &icirc;ncepuse anul cu un raliu puternic. Acesta a fost alimentat de optimismul investitorilor la schimbÄƒrile pozitive pe care administraÈ›ia Trump a susÈ›inut cÄƒ le va aduce &icirc;n industria cripto. TotuÈ™i, deÈ™i optimismul cu privire la implementarea unor reglementÄƒri prietenoase pentru cripto rÄƒm&acirc;ne, miÈ™cÄƒrile Bitcoin sunt &icirc;ncÄƒ dictate de tendinÈ›ele macroeconomice È™i teama investitorilor.\n\nParticipanÈ›ii de pe piaÈ›a cripto sunt &icirc;n aÈ™teptarea unui catalizator mai puternic care poate crea condiÈ›ii favorabile pentru a adÄƒuga active mai riscante &icirc;n propriul portofel criptomonede. MulÈ›i analiÈ™ti cripto cred cÄƒ Bitcoin se aflÄƒ acum &icirc;ntr-o corecÈ›ie ad&acirc;ncÄƒ. Istoric vorbind, unele corecÈ›ii de acest fel au condus la raliuri puternice de preÈ› dupÄƒ revenire. Astfel, susÈ›in cÄƒ Bitcoin &icirc;È™i va relua miÈ™carea ascendentÄƒ p&acirc;nÄƒ pe la mijlocul lunii martie.\n\nPentru cei care vor sÄƒ cumpere Bitcoin  &icirc;ntr-un mod sigur, fÄƒrÄƒ a investi sume mari de capital, BTC Bull pare o alternativÄƒ interesantÄƒ de investiÈ›ie. &Icirc;n mod similar, Best Wallet continuÄƒ sÄƒ atragÄƒ investitorii care cautÄƒ un portofel criptomonede inovativ pentru a-È™i stoca criptomonedele &icirc;n siguranÈ›Äƒ &icirc;nainte de urmÄƒtorul potenÈ›ial raliu dupÄƒ revenirea pieÈ›ei. HaideÈ›i sÄƒ vedem de ce aceste proiecte emergente capteazÄƒ atenÈ›ia investitorilor.\n\nVIZITEAZÄ‚ BITCOIN BULL\nATENÈšIE: InvestiÈ›iile &icirc;n criptomonede, &icirc;n special &icirc;n memecoin-uri, implicÄƒ riscuri extreme. PoÈ›i pierde &icirc;ntregul capital investit. Nu suntem experÈ›i financiari sau consultanÈ›i licenÈ›iaÈ›i. ConÈ›inutul acesta este informaÈ›ional È™i nu reprezintÄƒ sfat financiar, recomandare de investiÈ›ie sau &icirc;ncurajare de a cumpÄƒra. PieÈ›ele de criptomonede sunt foarte volatile È™i nereglementate. &Icirc;È›i recomandÄƒm sÄƒ nu investi niciodatÄƒ mai mult dec&acirc;t &icirc;È›i permiÈ›i sÄƒ pierzi.\n\nBTC Bull &ndash; o nouÄƒ erÄƒ pentru investitorii &icirc;n Bitcoin\nBTC Bull ($BTCBULL) se prezintÄƒ ca un meme coin oficial dedicat susÈ›inÄƒtorilor Bitcoin. Acesta combinÄƒ entuziasmul comunitÄƒÈ›ii cu recompensele. Lansat recent, proiectul a atras deja investiÈ›ii de peste 3 milioane de dolari &icirc;n prev&acirc;nzare. Succesul din presale evidenÈ›iazÄƒ &icirc;ncrederea È™i interesul crescut al investitorilor.\n\nUn aspect distinctiv al $BTCBULL este sistemul sÄƒu de recompense. DeÈ›inÄƒtorii tokenului $BTCBULL beneficiazÄƒ de airdrop-uri gratuite &icirc;n Bitcoin. Obiectivul proiectului este de a susÈ›ine creÈ™terea de preÈ› Bitcoin  p&acirc;nÄƒ la 250.000 de dolari È™i chiar mai mult. È˜i de a recompensa susÈ›inÄƒtorii Bitcoin &icirc;n cÄƒlÄƒtoria criptomonedei spre noi limite.', '1741013992bitcoin.png', '2025-03-03 14:59:52', 16, 16, 0, 'Bitcoin Reaches $100,000 â€“ Whatâ€™s Next?', 'Bitcoin Drops Below $90,000 â€“ Whatâ€™s Next and How to Take Advantage of the Marketâ€™s High Volatility\nThe crypto market crisis from earlier this week continues. Bitcoin has dropped below the $90,000 level. At the time of writing, the worldâ€™s most valuable cryptocurrency is trading at $88,430, down 3.67% in the past 24 hours.\n\nSource: Economica.net â€“ Wed, February 26, 2025, 3:19 PM\n\nBitcoin had kicked off the year with a strong rally, fueled by investor optimism over the positive changes promised by the Trump administration regarding the crypto industry.\nHowever, although optimism about crypto-friendly regulations remains, Bitcoin\'s movements are still heavily influenced by macroeconomic trends and investor fear.\n\nCrypto market participants are waiting for a stronger catalyst that could create favorable conditions to add more high-risk assets to their crypto portfolios. Many crypto analysts believe Bitcoin is currently in a deep correction. Historically, such corrections have often led to strong price rallies once the market recovers. As a result, many believe Bitcoin will resume its upward movement by mid-March.\n\nHow to Buy Bitcoin Safely During a Correction\nFor those looking to buy Bitcoin safely without investing large amounts of capital, BTC Bull seems to be an interesting alternative. Similarly, Best Wallet continues to attract investors seeking a secure and innovative crypto wallet to store their cryptocurrencies in preparation for the next potential rally.\n\nWARNING: Investing in cryptocurrencies, especially meme coins, involves extremely high risk. You can lose your entire investment. We are not financial advisors or licensed consultants. This content is for informational purposes only and does not constitute financial advice, investment recommendations, or encouragement to purchase. Crypto markets are highly volatile and unregulated. Never invest more than you can afford to lose.\n\nBTC Bull â€“ A New Era for Bitcoin Enthusiasts\nBTC Bull ($BTCBULL) presents itself as the official meme coin dedicated to Bitcoin supporters. It combines community enthusiasm with built-in rewards. Recently launched, the project has already raised over $3 million in its presale phase â€” a sign of growing investor interest and confidence.\n\nA distinctive feature of $BTCBULL is its reward system: holders of the $BTCBULL token receive free Bitcoin airdrops.\nThe projectâ€™s goal is to support Bitcoinâ€™s price growth up to